data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!! MOTIVATED SELLERS!!!  Welcome to charming Gulfport! This 2 bedroom, 1 bath gem is nestled in a private area, just steps away from the scenic Pinellas Trail. Located on a quiet street with only four homes, you'll enjoy the peace and tranquility that Gulfport has to offer. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a dining/kitchen combo offering plenty of space to entertain.  The adjacent living room is massive and is the perfect place to relax and unwind. The luxury vinyl flooring throughout adds a touch of elegance and durability to this beautiful home. Outback you will find a fully fenced backyard complete with custom wood deck, it is the perfect spot to enjoy a morning cup of coffee or your next BBQ. And with an inside laundry room, convenience is at your fingertips. Updates include a new roof in 2016 and HVAC system in 2021, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Updated 4-Point inspection report completed Nov 2022 is available.   With its prime location (NO FLOOD ZONE) less than 2 miles from historic Gulfport, you'll have easy access to the vibrant arts scene, delicious dining options, and picturesque waterfront views. Don't miss this incredible opportunity, schedule your showing today!
